snippet.title: Welcome to Woozworld
snippet.description: Get started with Woozworld, the fashion virtual world, and join millions of fashionistas (and fashionistos) personalizing and expressing styles with new weekly clothes, build your character’s story, and never get bored with thousands of stylish clothes that bring you one step closer to stardom!
